name: Ever Since Darwin "Fuel for the Denial Machine" cd
description: Get amped before a surf session with this octane-fueled high energy punk rock! Ever Since Darwin is a band entirely comprised of dropknee bodyboarders. This 6 song EP released in September 2012 is sure to have you fisting the air 1990s punk rock style and thinking Paul Roach still rides a Mach 7-SS in a fluro wetsuit! Fans of Bad Religion, Rise Against, Pennywise, Bouncing Souls, Millencolin and the Descendents are sure to love this CD. Also available asa digital download from iTunes and CD Baby.
